description: For over 20 years, El Olomega has been serving sensational home-style Salvadorian cuisine that the patrons of Red Hook Park simply adore. In addition, the cooks at El Olomega have served as a vital culinary contributor to the community, providing the people with legendarily delicious Pupusas, and other authentically marvelous meals,  alongside a laidback “siesta” feel that that fits right into the familial events at Red Hook Park (birthday parties, soccer games, etc..)Every New Yorker that has enjoyed this incredible mood-boosting food can attest that El Olomega is the “simply the best”.
name: El Olomega
